asset.hookText: Have Agenda 21-style programs infiltrated U.S. cities? Agenda 21 is an authoritarian violation of property rights and civil liberties that manipulates society through social engineering, and many cities around the U.S. have already implemented programs based on Agenda 21 principles. So what is the end game?
